data.description: This charming, well cared for, North Topeka home awaits you! It features two spacious bedrooms with ample closet space and one bathroom. The large living room provides room for entertaining. Off the kitchen is the laundry room leading to a brand-new patio which overlooks the spacious back yard. The attic and shed provide plenty of storage. All appliances remain with the home, including the washer and dryer. There have been many upgrades in recent years, including a new roof, newer windows, electrical, and plumbing. Book your tour today!
